  "comment": "Spectra 300 is a compact, LED-powered, CMY spot luminaire designed to provide immense output with an exceptionally wide zoom range that maintains a sharp focus with extensive colors and stunning effects to maximize functionality. Powered by a 300W LED engine, Spectra delivers bright, crisp projections with a 3.5deg - 46deg zoom range, complemented by an extensive color palette featuring CMY + CTO color mixing along with a dedicated 11-slot dichroic color wheel. Users can choose from 20 hand-selected gobos with auto-focus that can flood surfaces with sharp patterns and customize beams with iris and an 8-facet prism for uncompromised effects.",
